REQUIREMENTS:
	Because MPI usage is platform dependent, these environment variables
	    are used:
DOCK_PROCESSES  The number of MPI processes for DOCKing.
MPI_HOME        The path of the MPI installation.
	    If DOCK_PROCESSES is undefined then 2 is used.
	    If MPI_HOME is defined then the mpirun from that MPI bin
	    subdirectory is executed.
	    If MPI_HOME is undefined then mpirun is assumed to be in the PATH;
	    this is appropriate for platforms with native MPI.

TITLE: Contact Scoring

EXECUTABLES TESTED:
	dock6.mpi

FUNCTIONS TESTED:
	MPI Function

WALL CLOCK TIME:
	seconds

